---
title: Seared Pork & Homestyle Gravy with Mash & Roasted Veggies
description: This meal should be right at home at your place tonight. A nice piece of pork, smothered in a warm homestyle gravy and served with mashed potato and roasted veggies. Sometimes it’s hard to beat classic and simple.
